User routes
-> TO REGISTER: POST(/user/register)
Body: name, location (pass the coordinates)

-> TO Start trip: PUT(/user/start-trip)
Body: user(user object), distLimit(optional), endLocation(coordinates)

-> TO END trip: PUT(/user/register)
Body: user(user object)

Driver routes
-> TO REGISTER: POST(/driver/register)
Body: name, location (pass the coordinates)

-> To toggle driver availability: PUT(/driver/available)
Body: driverID(required), location(required if type is 'on'), type ('on' if availability is on)
